Package: MultiAmplicon
Title: Run metabarcoding alalyses for multiple amplicons
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Emanuel", "Heitlinger", email = "emanuelheitlinger@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The pagages allows to run a typical R/bioconductor workflow on
    multiple amplicons defined by different primer pairs (e.g. on the 16S or 18S
    genes and COI).
biocViews: Metagenomics,  Genetics, Sequencing, Microbiome,
    Metagenomics, Clustering, Classification, MultipleComparison,
    GeneticVariability
